extends email-layout

block content
  .subject
    h2 You just joined ChooseLife Email Subscribers List

  .body
    img(src="https://res.cloudinary.com/drnqdd87d/image/upload/q_auto,r_0/a_0/v1604448094/chooselife/shalom-mwenesi-JOx7sRRpqhI-unsplashchooselife-welcome.png", alt="welcome to chooselife")

    p Hello!,

    p You're welcome.

    p You requested to be added to the chooselife email subscribers list. Click on the link below to confirm your email.

    +button(activateLink, 'Activate new Subscribers List ->')

    p
      a(href=`${activateLink}`, target='_blank')= activateLink


    p If you didn't request this email, please ignore it.
    p Regards.
    p Choose Life Team.